{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"256452421b","title":"关于精兵简政问题给谢觉哉、陈正人的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e449c13cf","index":0,"year":1942,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"256452421b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"dbe0ec889c","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":16,"text":"谢觉哉，当时任中共中央西北局副书记、陕甘宁边区参议会副议长。陈正人（一九○七——一九七二），江西遂川人，当时任中共中央西北局组织部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6f5744b015","type":"title","text":"关于精兵简政问题给谢觉哉、陈正人的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"dbe0ec889c","type":"appellation","text":"觉哉、正人二同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"d21aa287c5","type":"paragraph","text":"今天所谈二届参议会应以准备精兵简政为中心，在开会以前应实行精简，开会以后应检查（点验）精简，而精简包括精少、效能、统一诸方面。今看本日（十九日）报纸《精兵简政在晋冀鲁豫边区》一文，所包事项尤多，尚有节省、反官僚主义诸项，此文我看很好，请你们也看一看，是否我们这里可以完全仿效？此事应在整风学习完后来一个如像整风这样的大举，方能普遍、深入与切实见效，过去还只是耳边风。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"7f3d73eba5","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"7bebc8d010","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"e003656b48","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"f78eebb62d","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"},{"id":"09fa936506","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b"}],"page":{"id":"7699b9d54a","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"256452421b","start":452,"end":452}}}},"__N_SSG":true}